{
  "name": "Seal Weaver",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/symbols/mask-metal-silver-white.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: General </p><p>You've practiced casting Jutsu in quick succession, learning techniques that grant you the following benefits: </p><p>• When you cast a Ninjutsu or Genjutsu with a casting time of 1 action, you may use your bonus action to cast a jutsu of the same type with the same casting time.</p><p>• When you cast a Ninjutsu or Genjutsu with a casting time of a bonus action, you can reduce the cost by half as long as it is no higher level than your highest rank known.</p><p>• Once you've used either effect of this feat twice, you must complete a long rest before you can use it again.</p><p></p>",
